cs2030.simulator

Class Statistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.Statistic

  • public class Statistic
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to generate statistics.

    Calling toString on a `Statistic` object will return a pretty string containing all the statistic associated with the object.
